[ Upstream commit cba6b758711cab946c787f7c15be92cc749b8e1f ]

This make use of hci_cmd_sync_queue for the following MGMT commands:

Add Advertising
Remove Advertising
Add Extended Advertising Parameters
Add Extended Advertising Data

